         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-12/screenshot_3.jpg?VersionId=BRouoAx..bFc8hpX4dYwTqsf5QNYe1Km&itok=q8BPJ5UK" alt="" data-caption="训练主要围绕舰机联合反潜、编队输送护航、海峡要道封锁等实战。（央视军事）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-12/screenshot_3.jpg?VersionId=BRouoAx..bFc8hpX4dYwTqsf5QNYe1Km&itok=q8BPJ5UK" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
      <figcaption><p>训练主要围绕舰机联合反潜、编队输送护航、海峡要道封锁等实战。（央视军事）</p></figcaption>
